# Pen tracks the polyline exactly via feedback linearisation. The body weaves
# underneath to make this happen — the pen path is the square, edges are
# straight, corners are sharp (within 1/120 s discretisation).
# Requires off-axis pen (px ≠ 0); fails for pen on the wheel-axis line.
speed 5

trace -30 0 -20 30 0 10
